{"about_the_game":"Planet Iridium is a third-person, top-down style game that sets focus<br />\r\non colonizing a planet called Planet B58, better known as Planet Iridium.<br />\r\nPlanet Iridium is a fantasy, sci-fi style game that focuses on multiple<br />\r\ngameplay aspects.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nOur end goal is to have 3 major storylines that will have their<br />\r\nown set of challenges and scenarios.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPlanet Iridium has 1 storyline available that's playable due to it being in Alpha.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIn this play-through your main objective is to restore a run-down, abandoned facility.<br />\r\nGather the necessary components to finally construct your very own colony.<br />\r\nWith the end goal being to set up a massive intergalactic trade route with Earth.<br />\r\nYou will also be challenged with having to fend off opposing raiders and bandits, while keeping Planet B58's inhabitants at bay.<br />\r\nIn this game you will also have to focus on farming, building, production, logistics and <br />\r\nyour very own players' survival, because even though this planet may appear all serene and breathtaking on the outside,<br />\r\nonce you look a little closer and stay a little longer, it will start to show you its true colours and secrets within.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&quot;No matter what, always remember, that you're never alone&quot;.","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2449270/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1693644617","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2449270/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1693644617","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2449270/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1693644617","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2449270/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1693644617","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptor